<div class="links topiclinks"><div class="inner">
<div class="title title-links"><h3><span class="title">Movimenti del mouse</span></h3></div>
<div class="region"><ul>
<li class="links ">
<a href="mouse-sensitivity.html.it" title="Adjust the speed of the mouse and touchpad">Adjust the speed of the mouse and touchpad</a><span class="desc"> — Modificare quanto rapidamente si sposta il puntatore del mouse quando si usa il mouse o il touchpad.</span>
</li>
<li class="links ">
<a href="mouse-mousekeys.html.it" title="Click and move the mouse pointer using the keypad">Click and move the mouse pointer using the keypad</a><span class="desc"> — Enable mouse keys to control the mouse with the numeric
